OL,3,CFormer hospital bosses admit they
OL,4,Cwould not choose on-island healthcare
OL,6,FThree former senior members of
OL,7,FJersey's Health Department have given
OL,8,Fa damning account of the health
OL,9,Fservice and admit they would be
OL,10,Freluctant to receive care on the
OL,11,Fisland.
OL,13,FProfessor Simon Mackenzie, Tom Hayhoe
OL,14,Fand Hugo Mascie-Taylor spoke at three
OL,15,Fpublic hearings organised by Jersey's
OL,16,FHealth and Social Security (HSS)
OL,17,FScrutiny Panel this week.
