OL,3,CFormer hospital bosses admit they
OL,4,Cwould not choose on-island healthcare
OL,6,FTogether, they shared concerns over
OL,7,Fpatient safety, a toxic working
OL,8,Fculture within the service and a
OL,9,Fresistance to change.
OL,11,FMr Hayhoe was the Chair of Jersey's
OL,12,FHealth Advisory Board for a month
OL,13,Fbefore stepping down. Mr Mascie-Taylor
OL,14,Fwas Interim Chair of the board in 2022
OL,15,Fand Professor Mackenzie joined the
OL,16,FHealth Change Team as Clinical Lead in
OL,17,F2023.
