OL,3,CFormer hospital bosses admit they
OL,4,Cwould not choose on-island healthcare
OL,6,FThe panel was chaired by Deputy Louise
OL,7,FDoublet and Deputy Jonathan Renouf.
OL,8,FOther members included: Deputy Sir
OL,9,FPhilip Bailhache and Deputy Lucy
OL,10,FStephenson.
OL,12,FFormer Chair of Jersey's Health
OL,13,FAdvisory Board, Tom Hayhoe said he was
OL,14,F"acutely aware many issues around
OL,15,Fpatient safety."
OL,17,FA culture of 'covering things up' was
OL,18,Falso raised during the meeting, where
OL,19,Fit was highlighted that rather than
OL,20,Freporting when things go wrong, they
OL,21,Fare hidden.
