OL,3,CFormer hospital bosses admit they
OL,4,Cwould not choose on-island healthcare
OL,6,FProfessor Simon Mackenzie and Tom
OL,7,FHayhoe also shared their reluctance to
OL,8,Freceive care in Jersey.
OL,10,FCurrent member of Jersey's Health
OL,11,FScrutiny Panel, Deputy Johnathan
OL,12,FRenouf says the revelations are
OL,13,Fshocking: "Things are so serious that
OL,14,Fthey would not take care in Jersey as
OL,15,Fa first choice.
OL,17,F"That is a damning indictment to hear
OL,18,Ffrom those who have been at the top of
OL,19,Fan organisation."
