OL,3,CFormer hospital bosses admit they
OL,4,Cwould not choose on-island healthcare
OL,6,FIn response, Health Minister Deputy
OL,7,FTom Binet says: "One of them has 4
OL,8,Fweeks part-time experience and
OL,9,Fprobably spent less than a few hours
OL,10,Fin the hospital, and the other one was
OL,11,Fresponsible for putting the job right
OL,12,Fover the last 12 months.
OL,14,F"On a personal level, if I get ill,
OL,15,FI'm quite happy to use the services
OL,16,Fthat are here, bearing in mind I know
OL,17,Fthere are some problems. But there are
OL,18,Fpeople trying to put that right and
OL,19,Fthere are a lot of people doing a
OL,20,Freally job and this has done nothing
OL,21,Ffor morale."
