OL,3,CFormer hospital bosses admit they
OL,4,Cwould not choose on-island healthcare
OL,6,FThese issues and the culture within
OL,7,Fthe health department were raised in
OL,8,F2022 by Mr Mascie-Taylor.
OL,10,FHowever, all three senior members
OL,11,Fshared that no change had been
OL,12,Fachieved and doing so would take a
OL,13,Fhuge amount of effort and
OL,14,Fdetermination.
OL,16,FDeputy Binet says it will be a
OL,17,Ffailure, on his part, if these issues
OL,18,Fstill exist in two years time.
